Due to a lot of error reports related to autoconf/automake that
I've received, the configuration script is now to be run as
'scripts/configure' instead of './configure'.

********************************************************************************

Shortcuts for GL widget
-----------------------

Left Arrow - move image for N pixels right
Right Arrow - move image for N pixels left
Up Arrow  - move image for N pixels down
Down Arrow  - move image for N pixels up
Plus/Minus - zoom Nx
Ctrl + Plus/Minus - zoom 2x or 0.5x
V - flip vertically
H - flip horizontally
Ctrl + Left Arrow - rotate left for N degrees
Ctrl + Right Arrow - rotate right for N degrees
Ctrl + Up/Down Arrow - rotate for 180' degrees up/down
Shift + Up/Down Arrow - rotate for 1' degree up/down
R - Reset
Ctrl + R - Render into file
Space - next image
Backspace - previous image
Home - first image
End - last image
Esc,X - Close
P - image properties
Q - Quick Browser
F - Fullscreen

******************

N - can be set throw 'Options'
